summary: The Goddess of Beauty has appeared on Nirn.. as a undead lady
descriptionHtml:
Meet Dibella.

She has appeared along side a new Dibellan Shrine just located outside Whiterun for yall to worship and make out/snog/kiss infront of. She is a companion and should be UFO friendly

Dibella is a custom Draugr retexture that is stand-alone and does not overite anyother textures so should be completely compatable with any other Draugr mods.

Dibella can shout and use magic e.g. ebodyflesh to protect her self.

....and she is nude... >.>
author: Beth
